    "name": "Kitsune's Paths Tower Defense",
    "steam_appid": 3287330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras/f9bb680e951d43c8d9c6d4deb677df7a.avif?t=1744217951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras_big/f9bb680e951d43c8d9c6d4deb677df7a.avif?t=1744217951 width=800 height=165 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于《Kitsune's Paths》：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《<strong>Kitsune's Paths</strong>》中，你将扮演<strong>善狐（Zenko）</strong>：<br>一只守护森林的狐狸，负责保护引导善良灵魂进入下一个灵界的传送门。运用你的魔法力量、速度和智慧，激活沿途的防御塔，阻止恶魔穿越传送门，并逐渐成长为传说中的九尾狐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras/da6257f34193b8e589108bc13560edea.avif?t=1744217951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras_big/da6257f34193b8e589108bc13560edea.avif?t=1744217951 width=800 height=156 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制定你的策略：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款塔防游戏中，你将成为主角。探索地图，根据不同敌人的类型，合理点亮防御塔，制定最佳防御策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras/ee93b6a00cbd3383094772911e6388cf.avif?t=1744217951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras_big/ee93b6a00cbd3383094772911e6388cf.avif?t=1744217951 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>施放新法术：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新技能，提升角色等级。完整版游戏将提供技能树，让你自由升级所选法术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras/c0871d7a8e3ad2adce5de4a403d47e45.avif?t=1744217951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras_big/c0871d7a8e3ad2adce5de4a403d47e45.avif?t=1744217951 width=800 height=203 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>守护世界：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战高难度关卡，探索新世界，帮助更多善良灵魂通过鸟居（Torii）。每成功守护一个世界，你都会获得一条新的尾巴，最终化身为神话中的九尾狐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可能感兴趣的内容：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整版将包含 24 个关卡（可能会增加额外内容）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 种防御塔，可升级至 3 级，并可根据 5 种元素进行自定义。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善狐的全新技能与能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 个独特世界，全部采用手绘背景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >17 种独特敌人，皆为妖怪恶魔。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的善良灵魂会在旅途中给予帮助。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras/42b71beb09a7008392a76b0f59edf513.avif?t=1744217951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287330/extras_big/42b71beb09a7008392a76b0f59edf513.avif?t=1744217951 width=800 height=524 /></span></p>",
